West_Allis.WNRG-FM: WNRG-FM (106.9 FM) - branded as "Energy 106.9" - is a rhythmic contemporary radio station in Milwaukee, Wisconsin, licensed to the suburb of Brookfield. The station, which is owned by Saga Communications, is branded as "Energy 106.9". Its studios (which are shared with the other four sister stations) and transmitter are located in Milwaukee's West Side.
